  "detailed_description": "<h1>Another Horror Tale Games</h1><p><strong></strong><br><strong></strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levana is a psychological horror game where you experience the perspective of an astronaut on the moon</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141360/extras/f797f5a087c607536cd8bdf5858ae7cf.poster.avif?t=1764201783\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141360/extras/f797f5a087c607536cd8bdf5858ae7cf.webm?t=1764201783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141360/extras/f797f5a087c607536cd8bdf5858ae7cf.mp4?t=1764201783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levana</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Levana</strong>, you are in your ship and must go out to perform various tasks as commanded over the radio. You can use different objects to complete these tasks, and you must be careful as there are things <strong>you haven't been informed about</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levana is a photorealistic first-person simulator with various mechanics to complete tasks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric environment and photorealistic graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro VHS aesthetic</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game only supports 16:9 proportional resolutions (Not ultrawide)</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levana is a psychological horror game where you experience the perspective of an astronaut on the moon</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141360/extras/f797f5a087c607536cd8bdf5858ae7cf.poster.avif?t=1764201783\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141360/extras/f797f5a087c607536cd8bdf5858ae7cf.webm?t=1764201783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141360/extras/f797f5a087c607536cd8bdf5858ae7cf.mp4?t=1764201783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levana</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Levana</strong>, you are in your ship and must go out to perform various tasks as commanded over the radio. You can use different objects to complete these tasks, and you must be careful as there are things <strong>you haven't been informed about</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levana is a photorealistic first-person simulator with various mechanics to complete tasks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric environment and photorealistic graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro VHS aesthetic</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game only supports 16:9 proportional resolutions (Not ultrawide)</p>",
